In [21]:
def load_mnist():
    f = gzip.open("mnist/mnist.pkl.gz", 'rb')
    train, valid, test = load(f, encoding='latin1')
    f.close()
    return train[0][:20000],train[1][:20000]
In [22]:
# Get data
X, y = load_mnist()
map_size = [20,20]
cl = som.SOM(map_size[0], map_size[1])
cl.train(X, 5000)
In [23]:
# Plotting hidden units
W = cl.map
W = make_tile(W, img_shape= (28,28), tile_shape=(map_size[0], map_size[1]))
img = Image.fromarray(W)
plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
plt.imshow(img, cmap='gray'); plt.axis('off');
img.save("som_results.png")
